                                         "responseBody":  "\u003c!DOCTYPE html\u003e\n\u003chtml lang=\"es\"\u003e\n\u003chead\u003e\n\u003cmeta charset=\"UTF-8\"\u003e\n\u003cmeta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\"\u003e\n\u003ctitle\u003eHooklight | Capacitacion Anti-Phishing\u003c/title\u003e\n\u003clink rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com\"\u003e\n\u003clink rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.gstatic.com\" crossorigin\u003e\n\u003clink href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Manrope:wght@400;600;700;800\u0026display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\"\u003e\n\u003cstyle\u003e\n    :root {\n        --brand-900: #0f2748;\n        --brand-700: #1e4b84;\n        --accent-500: #f4a261;\n        --danger-700: #b42318;\n        --danger-100: #ffeceb;\n        --ok-50: #eef7ff;\n        --text-main: #11243f;\n        --text-soft: #4b5d78;\n        --card: #ffffff;\n    }\n\n    * { box-sizing: border-box; }\n\n    body {\n        margin: 0;\n        font-family: \"Manrope\", \"Segoe UI\", sans-serif;\n        color: var(--text-main);\n        background: radial-gradient(circle at 20% 0%, #f7fbff 0%, #eef4ff 45%, #e9f1ff 100%);\n        min-height: 100vh;\n        display: flex;\n        align-items: center;\n        justify-content: center;\n        padding: 24px;\n    }\n\n    .container {\n        width: 100%;\n        max-width: 920px;\n        background: var(--card);\n        border-radius: 20px;\n        border: 1px solid #d9e5f8;\n        box-shadow: 0 22px 50px rgba(16, 44, 83, 0.14);\n        overflow: hidden;\n    }\n\n    .top-band {\n        padding: 18px 28px;\n        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #132a4a 0%, #204f8c 100%);\n        color: #f8fcff;\n        font-size: 14px;\n        letter-spacing: 0.2px;\n        text-align: center;\n    }\n\n    .content {\n        padding: 34px;\n    }\n\n    .header {\n        text-align: center;\n        margin-bottom: 20px;\n    }\n\n    .logo {\n        height: 52px;\n        object-fit: contain;\n        margin-bottom: 14px;\n    }\n\n    h1 {\n        margin: 0;\n        font-size: 34px;\n        line-height: 1.15;\n        color: var(--brand-900);\n    }\n\n    .alert {\n        margin: 18px auto 22px;\n        padding: 16px 18px;\n        border-radius: 12px;\n        border: 1px solid #fecaca;\n        background: var(--danger-100);\n        color: var(--danger-700);\n        font-weight: 700;\n        text-align: center;\n    }\n\n    .intro {\n        margin: 0 auto 26px;\n        max-width: 760px;\n        text-align: center;\n        color: var(--text-soft);\n        font-size: 17px;\n        line-height: 1.7;\n    }\n\n    .sales-highlight {\n        margin: 0 auto 28px;\n        max-width: 760px;\n        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #0f2748 0%, #1d4d86 100%);\n        color: #f7fbff;\n        border-radius: 14px;\n        padding: 18px 20px;\n        text-align: center;\n        font-weight: 600;\n    }\n\n    .grid {\n        display: grid;\n        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));\n        gap: 18px;\n        margin-bottom: 26px;\n    }\n\n    .card {\n        background: var(--ok-50);\n        border: 1px solid #d7e8ff;\n        border-radius: 14px;\n        padding: 20px;\n    }\n\n    .card h3 {\n        margin: 0 0 12px;\n        color: var(--brand-900);\n        font-size: 20px;\n    }\n\n    ul {\n        margin: 0;\n        padding-left: 18px;\n        color: #23395b;\n        line-height: 1.7;\n        font-size: 15px;\n    }\n\n    .cta {\n        display: flex;\n        gap: 12px;\n        justify-content: center;\n        flex-wrap: wrap;\n        margin-top: 8px;\n    }\n\n    .btn {\n        display: inline-flex;\n        align-items: center;\n        justify-content: center;\n        text-decoration: none;\n        border-radius: 10px;\n        padding: 14px 24px;\n        font-weight: 700;\n        transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;\n    }\n\n    .btn-primary {\n        background: #f4a261;\n        color: #1d1a17;\n        box-shadow: 0 10px 22px rgba(244, 162, 97, 0.38);\n    }\n\n    .btn-secondary {\n        background: #e7effd;\n        color: #12305a;\n        border: 1px solid #ccdcf8;\n    }\n\n    .btn:hover {\n        transform: translateY(-2px);\n    }\n\n    .footer {\n        margin-top: 22px;\n        text-align: center;\n        font-size: 13px;\n        color: #70829c;\n    }\n\n    @media (max-width: 760px) {\n        .content { padding: 22px; }\n        h1 { font-size: 28px; }\n        .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\n    }\n\u003c/style\u003e\n\u003c/head\u003e\n\u003cbody\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"container\"\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class=\"top-band\"\u003eSimulacion completada. Ahora es momento de convertir el riesgo en prevencion real.\u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class=\"content\"\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"header\"\u003e\n            \u003cimg src=\"https://hooklight-thesis.pages.dev/hooklogo.png\" alt=\"Hooklight Logo\" class=\"logo\"\u003e\n            \u003ch1\u003eTu equipo puede evitar el proximo incidente\u003c/h1\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n        \u003cdiv class=\"alert\"\u003eDetectamos un clic en una simulacion de phishing. No hay sancion: hay oportunidad de mejora.\u003c/div\u003e\n\n        \u003cp class=\"intro\"\u003e\n            En Hooklight ayudamos a empresas a reducir errores humanos con entrenamientos practicos, medibles y orientados a resultados.\n            Cada persona que aprende a detectar un engano digital protege datos, dinero y reputacion de toda la organizacion.\n        \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003cdiv class=\"sales-highlight\"\u003e\n            Programa recomendado: Capacitacion Anti-Phishing para colaboradores, con modulos breves, evaluaciones y reportes para RRHH, IT y Compliance.\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n        \u003cdiv class=\"grid\"\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"card\"\u003e\n                \u003ch3\u003eRiesgos que evitamos\u003c/h3\u003e\n                \u003cul\u003e\n                    \u003cli\u003eRobo de credenciales y acceso no autorizado.\u003c/li\u003e\n                    \u003cli\u003eFraude por suplantacion de identidad (BEC).\u003c/li\u003e\n                    \u003cli\u003eFiltracion de datos sensibles y multas regulatorias.\u003c/li\u003e\n                    \u003cli\u003eInterrupciones operativas por malware o ransomware.\u003c/li\u003e\n                \u003c/ul\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"card\"\u003e\n                \u003ch3\u003eLo que incluye la capacitacion\u003c/h3\u003e\n                \u003cul\u003e\n                    \u003cli\u003eSimulaciones reales por area y nivel de riesgo.\u003c/li\u003e\n                    \u003cli\u003eMicro-lecciones para respuesta inmediata.\u003c/li\u003e\n                    \u003cli\u003eMetricas de avance por equipos y usuarios.\u003c/li\u003e\n                    \u003cli\u003ePlan de mejora continua con acompanamiento Hooklight.\u003c/li\u003e\n                \u003c/ul\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n        \u003cdiv class=\"cta\"\u003e\n            \u003ca class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"https://hooklight-thesis.pages.dev\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"\u003eComprar capacitacion\u003c/a\u003e\n            \u003ca class=\"btn btn-secondary\" href=\"https://hooklight-thesis.pages.dev\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"\u003eConocer Hooklight\u003c/a\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n        \u003cdiv class=\"footer\"\u003eHooklight | Cultura de ciberseguridad para empresas - 2026\u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/body\u003e\n\u003c/html\u003e",
